\c 14
\s Karebhu anopiwa Hebhuroni
\p
\v 1 Zvino idzi \add inzvimbo\add* vana vaIsraeri dzavakagara nhaka panyika yeKenani, Eriazari mupristi naJoshua mwanakomana waNuni nemisoro yemadzibaba yemarudzi evana vaIsraeri dzavakagovera\x + Num.. 34.17,18.\x*
\v 2 nemujenya wenhaka yavo; Jehovha sezvaakaraira neruoko rwaMozisi, pamarudzi mapfumbamwe nehafu yerudzi\x + Num.. 26.55. 33.54. 34.13. Vato. 20.9.\x*.
\v 3 Nokuti Mozisi waiva apa nhaka marudzi maviri nehafu yerudzi mhiri kwaJoridhani; asi kuVaRevhi haana kupa nhaka pakati pawo\x + 13.7,8,32,33.\x*.
\v 4 Nokuti vana vaJosefa vaiva marudzi maviri: Manase naEfuremu\x + Gen.. 48.5. 1 Makor. 5.1,2.\x*. Zvino havana kupa VaRevhi mugove munyika, kunze kwemaguta ekugara, nemafuro awo ezvipfuwo zvavo neefuma yavo\x + Gen.. 34.23; 36.6.\x*.
\v 5 Jehovha sezvaakaraira Mozisi, vana vaIsraeri vakaita saizvozvo, ndokukamura nyika\x + Num.. 35.2; 21.2.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Ipapo vana vaJudha vakaswedera kuna Joshua paGirigari; Karebhu mwanakomana waJefune, muKenizi ndokuti kwaari\x + Num.. 32.12; Josh. 14.14; 15.17.\x*: Iwe unoziva shoko Jehovha raakataura kuna Mozisi\x + Num.. 14.30. Det. 1.36,38.\x* munhu waMwari maererano neni uye maererano newe paKadheshi-Bharineya\x + Det. 33.1.\x*.
\v 7 Ndaiva nemakore makumi mana Mozisi muranda waMwari paakandituma kubva paKadheshi-Bharineya kunoshora nyika. Ndikadzosa kwaari shoko sezvaiva mumoyo mangu\x + Num.. 13.6,26; 14.6.\x*.
\v 8 Asi hama dzangu dzaiva dzakwira neni\x + Det. 1.28.\x* dzakanyungudusa\x + Det. 1.28.\x* moyo yevanhu; asi ini ndakatevera Jehovha Mwari wangu zvakazara\x + Num.. 14.24. Det. 1.36.\x*.
\v 9 Zvino Mozisi wakapika nezuva iro achiti: Zvirokwazvo nyika\x + Num.. 14.23,24. Det. 1.36. 1.3.\x* tsoka yako yayakatsika ichava nhaka yako neyevana vako nekusingaperi\x + Num.. 13.22.\x*, nokuti wakatevera Jehovha Mwari wangu zvakazara\x + Num.. 14.24. Det. 1.36.\x*.
\v 10 Zvino ikozvino tarira, Jehovha wakandichengeta ndiri mupenyu sezvaakareva, makore awa makumi mana nemashanu kubva Jehovha paakataura shoko iri kuna Mozisi, Israeri achafamba murenje\x + Num.. 14.30.\x*. Zvino ikozvino, tarira, nhasi ndine makore makumi masere nemashanu\x + Josh. 14.7.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Nhasi ndichakasimba sepazuva Mozisi raakandituma\x + Det. 34.7.\x*; sesimba rangu nenguva iyo, rakadaro simba rangu ikozvino, rehondo, nerekubuda, nerekupinda\x + Det. 31.2.\x*.
\v 12 Naizvozvo zvino, ndipe nyika iyi yezvikomo, Jehovha yaakareva nezuva iro, nokuti iwe wakanzwa nezuva iro kuti VaAnaki vaiva varipo nemaguta makuru akashoshewa\x + Num.. 13.28,33.\x*; zvimwe Jehovha achava neni, ipapo ndichavadzingira kunze, Jehovha sezvaakareva.
\v 13 Zvino Joshua wakamuropafadza\x + 22.6.\x* ndokupa kuna Karebhu mwanakomana waJefune Hebhuroni kuva nhaka\x + 10.36,37. 15.14. Vato. 1.20. 1 Makor. 6.56.\x*.
\v 14 Naizvozvo Hebhuroni rakava nhaka yaKarebhu mwanakomana waJefune muKenizi kusvika nhasi; nokuti waiva achitevera Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri\x + 14.8,9.\x* zvakazara.
\v 15 Zvino zita reHebhuroni pakutanga raiva Kiriyati-Aribha; iye waiva munhu mukuru pakati pevaAnaki\x + 21.11.\x*. Nyika ndokuzorora pahondo\x + 11.23.\x*.